She Was Pretty is a 2015 South Korean television series starring Hwang Jung-eum , Park Seo-joon , Go Joon-hee , and Choi Si-won .
It reunited Hwang Jung-eum with Park Seo-joon , who previously starred together in Kill Me , Heal Me ; and Hwang Jung-eum with Go Joon-hee , who previously starred together in Can You Hear My Heart .
